OL,3,CFamily say arson attack deaths 'wholly
OL,4,Cpreventable'
OL,6,FThe family of a mother and four of her
OL,7,Fchildren murdered in an arson attack
OL,8,Fin Greater Manchester believes their
OL,9,Fdeaths were "wholly preventable", a
OL,10,Fcourt has heard.
OL,12,FThe blaze claimed the lives of Demi
OL,13,FPearson, 15, her brother Brandon,
OL,14,Feight, and sisters Lacie, seven, and
OL,15,FLia, three.
OL,17,FTheir mother Michelle Pearson suffered
OL,18,F68% burns to her body and "clung on to
OL,19,Flife" until she died, aged 37, on
OL,20,FAugust 25 2019 ` 20 months after the
OL,21,Fattack in Walkden.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@`O]zD@[OU{D@EO]
