OL,6,FShe had "begged" to be rehoused and
OL,7,Fcalled police on five occasions in the
OL,8,Ftwo weeks before the fatal attack, the
OL,9,Ftrial of her killers heard.
OL,11,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,12,FConduct (IOPC) investigated the
OL,13,Ffamily's contact with Greater
OL,14,FManchester Police (GMP) involving
OL,15,Fincidents and threats from their
OL,16,Fkillers, and a report was completed in
OL,17,F2019, but not made public.
OL,26,@nD@IOUnD@PO]
