OL,6,FOn Wednesday a pre-inquest hearing
OL,7,Ftook place at Bolton Coroner's Court,
OL,8,Fmore than seven years on from the
OL,9,Fdeaths.
OL,11,FA full inquest is scheduled for June
OL,12,Fthis year, but this is now in doubt,
OL,13,Fthe hearing was told.
OL,15,FGlynis Craig, representing the IOPC,
OL,16,Ftold the hearing the police watchdog
OL,17,Fhad been notified by GMP of "some
OL,18,Fconcerns" around the IOPC original
OL,19,Finvestigation and had asked it to
OL,20,Freview it.
OL,26,@yD@]OUzD@IO]
