OL,6,FThe IOPC was now deciding, following
OL,7,Fthe review, whether it needed to
OL,8,Fconduct a new investigation, Ms Craig
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FTimothy Brennand, senior coroner for
OL,12,FGreater Manchester West, told Ms Craig
OL,13,Fthat if ever there was a case that
OL,14,Fmerited more resources to prevent
OL,15,Ffurther delay, "this is the case".
OL,17,FMr Brennand said the Pearson family
OL,18,Fwishes to know whether any possible
OL,19,Ffailures by the police or other local
OL,20,Fauthorities put the family at risk.
OL,26,@wD@POUwD@aO]
