OL,6,FHe added: "The family have raised
OL,7,Fserious misgivings of missed
OL,8,Fopportunities for state agencies to
OL,9,Fhave adequately assessed the risk to
OL,10,Flife and take appropriate action.
OL,12,F"The family contend the deaths to be
OL,13,Fwholly preventable and were not
OL,14,Fsufficiently involved in the
OL,15,Fsubsequent investigations, have no
OL,16,Fconfidence in findings, some of which
OL,17,Fare not within the public domain as
OL,18,Fyet..."
