OL,6,FZak Bolland and David Worrall were
OL,7,Fboth given four life sentences and
OL,8,Ftold they would serve a minimum of 40
OL,9,Fand 37 years respectively for the
OL,10,Fpetrol bomb attack on the Pearson
OL,11,Ffamily home on Jackson Street in
OL,12,FWalkden in the early hours of December
OL,13,F11 2017.
OL,15,FBolland's girlfriend, Courtney
OL,16,FBrierley, 20, was jailed for 21 years
OL,17,Ffor four counts of manslaughter after
OL,18,Fthe trial at Manchester Crown Court in
OL,19,F2018.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
