OL,6,FA major safeguarding review was
OL,7,Flaunched into how authorities,
OL,8,Fincluding the council, police and
OL,9,Fhealth officials, handled contact with
OL,10,Fthe family before the fatal attack.
OL,12,FThis review has also not been made
OL,13,Fpublic.
OL,15,FMrs Pearson's home was previously
OL,16,Fattacked, its windows and doors
OL,17,Fsmashed, graffiti sprayed on the walls
OL,18,Fand her wheelie bin set on fire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
