OL,6,FShe saw at least six different
OL,7,Fofficers, statements were made, risk
OL,8,Freferral forms completed, fire service
OL,9,Fpersonnel carried out two "safe and
OL,10,Fwell" visits, the family social worker
OL,11,Fwas informed and social services were
OL,12,Falerted.
OL,14,FMrs Pearson told her housing provider,
OL,15,FCity West, she did not feel safe at
OL,16,Fhome with her children and wanted out.
OL,18,FCity West said it never received any
OL,19,Frequest for a move, believed to have
OL,20,Fbeen handled by Salford City Council.
