OL,6,FOfficers from GMP took a statement
OL,7,Ffrom Mrs Pearson on the night of the
OL,8,Ffire, having been called out after
OL,9,FBolland had been round "kicking off".
OL,11,FIt is not clear if officers
OL,12,Fimmediately actively sought out
OL,13,FBolland, who lived around 300 yards
OL,14,Ffrom Mrs Pearson and was at home at
OL,15,Fthe time the officers called.
OL,17,FHours later he and Worrall returned to
OL,18,Fthe Pearsons' home armed with two
OL,19,Fpetrol bombs.
